title: Chelsea vs Liverpool - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Chelsea are winless in their last 10 meetings with Liverpool in all competitions, only once before going longer without a win over the Reds. After their 2-1 win in October, Liverpool are looking to complete their first league double over Chelsea since their title-winning 2019-20 campaign. Arne Slot could become only the third Reds boss to win both of his first two league games against Chelsea in charge of the club, after Bill Shankly and Roy Evans.

title: Arsenal vs AFC Bournemouth- English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Arsenal have won all eight of their home games against Bournemouth in all competitions, scoring 23 goals and conceding just four. title: Brighton and Hove Albion vs Newcastle United - English Premier League 2024/2025

title: Bayern Munchen vs Borussia Monchengladbach - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: FC Bayern Munchen have won three consecutive Bundesliga games against Borussia Monchengladbach for the first time since between 2013 and 2014. Overall, no other side in league history has as many wins against FCB as Gladbach do. FC Bayern Munchen are German champions for the 34th time. It means they will end the season having topped the table for 32 of the 34 matchdays, something they last managed in 2012/13 under Jupp Heynckes. title: La Liga ROAD TO ELCLÁSICO EP3
description: In Road to ElClásico we’ll look back at both teams’ paths up to this point, reliving FC Barcelona and Real Madrid’s most spectacular and crucial performances. We will relive all these encounters in detail, with a carefully crafted montage and a cinematic look.

title: La Liga ELCLÁSICO, THE MOVIE EP1
description: Kylian Mbappe and Lamine Yamal were the stars of the first LALIGA EA Sports ElClásico of the season. The former, a new signing for Real Madrid, was making his first appearance in this showcase fixture. And the latter was leading FC Barcelona after triumphing at the summers European Championship. The ElClásico film delves into the careers of both players, revealing their origins and their lives off the pitch, and follows their performances in detail during LALIGAs most anticipated football event.

title: La Liga ELCLÁSICO ANALYSIS EP2
description: In this edition of ElClásico Analysis, we’ll dissect all previous meetings between both managers, their most important players, key tactical aspects, and stats to try to get an idea of what we canexpect from this mouth-watering encounter. All with the help of LALIGA’s state-of-the-art technology, such as Libero Vision, and the most spectacular images. As well as the most detailed statistics of both teams and all their players, thanks to the analysis software Mediacoach, and direct testimonies from the key figures of Spanish football’s major Clásico.

title: Brest vs Lille - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 33
description: Brest have won just 19% of their games against Lille in Ligue 1, only having a lower win percentage against Paris SG amongst teams they’ve faced 10+ times in the division. Brest have picked up 47 points after 32 games in Ligue 1 2024-25, 10 fewer than at this same stage last season, but this represents their second-highest tally at this point in the championship. Certain to finish between eighth and tenth place, the Breton club will establish its second-best Ligue 1 ranking of the 21st century.

title: AFC Bournemouth vs Aston Villa - English Premier League 2024/25 Week 37
description: Bournemouth lost 1-0 at home to Aston Villa in their first ever Premier League match in August 2015. title: Ipswich Town vs Brentford - English Premier League 2024/25 Week 37
description: Ipswich have won just one of their last 10 league games against Brentford, a 2-0 home win in August 2017. This is the first time they’re hosting the Bees since a 1-1 draw in September 2018 in the Championship. Following their 4-3 win at the Gtech Community Stadium in October, Brentford are looking to complete a league double over Ipswich for the first time.

title: Atletico Madrid vs Real Sociedad - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 35
description: Atletico de Madrid have not lost any of their last 10 LaLiga matches against Real Sociedad, since a 0-2 defeat in September 2019, their longest unbeaten run against the San Sebastian side in the competition since April 1976. At home, Atletico de Madrid have not lost in their last 11 LaLiga matches against Real Sociedad, since a 0-1 defeat in March 2013, scoring exactly two goals in six of the last seven.

title: Valencia vs Getafe - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 35
description: Valencia have won only four of their last 17 LaLiga matches against Getafe, after winning 12 of their previous 16 top-flight matches. title: La Liga ELCLÁSICO ANALYSIS EP2
description: In this edition of ElClásico Analysis, we’ll dissect all previous meetings between both managers, their most important players, key tactical aspects, and stats to try to get an idea of what we canexpect from this mouth-watering encounter. As well as the most detailed statistics of both teams and all their players, thanks to the analysis software Mediacoach, and direct testimonies from the key figures of Spanish football’s major Clásico.

title: Union Berlin vs Heidenheim - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: 1. FC Union Berlin are without a win in their last nine league games against 1. FC Heidenheim. Since beating FCH 1-0 in April 2016 in the second division, Union have won just one of the last 10 competitive meetings: a 2-0 victory in the second round of the DFB-Pokal in 2022/23. FCU are yet to beat FCH in the top flight – the only other current Bundesliga side they have never beaten is FC Bayern. 1. FC Union Berlin are unbeaten in their last eight Bundesliga games, the longest ongoing run in the league. They have equalled their club record for a single top-flight season, only previously achieved between September and November 2020 under Urs Fischer.

title: Holstein Kiel vs Freiburg - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: SC Freiburg and Holstein Kiel have only previously met twice in professional football. The Storks won 2-1 at home in the second round of the 2018/19 DFB-Pokal, while Freiburg secured a 3-2 home victory earlier this season. SC Freiburg have only won one of their last seven Bundesliga games away at league debutants : 2-1 at Greuther Furth in May 2013. They have lost each of their last three such fixtures, scoring two goals and conceding nine. Their most recent trip to a top-flight debutant saw them lose 3-2 in Heidenheim last season.

title: Werder Bremen vs RB Leipzig - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: RB Leipzig are unbeaten in their last 10 competitive games against SV Werder Bremen, winning eight of them. Of teams currently in the top flight that they have faced more than four times, Leipzig’s points-per-game average against SVW isn’t higher against any other side. SV Werder Bremen sit in eighth place with 47 points – they last had more points after 32 Bundesliga games in 2009/10 when they last qualified for Europe. SVW are three points behind sixth-placed RB Leipzig – since the introduction of three points per win, only Karlsruher SC in 1996/97 and Hamburger SV in 1995/96 have ever made up as large a gap to sixth over the last two matchdays.

title: Bochum vs Mainz 05 - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33

Only VfL Wolfsburg are currently on a longer wait for a Bundesliga win than VfL Bochum and 1. FSV Mainz 05. This is Mainz’s longest spell without victory since between November 2023 and February 2024.

description: Three strikers, three stories, one common goal: scoring goals for the teams success. But what shaped Harry Kane, Patrik Schick, and Hugo Ekitike on their paths to the top? In the 26-minute documentary Roots – Kane, Schick and Ekitike, we travel back to the beginnings of these Bundesliga stars. For FC Bayern Munchen player Harry Kane, we trace his roots in Chingford, a suburban town in East London. We also speak with youth coaches from his first club, Ridgeway Rovers, as well as former Tottenham player and England international Jermain Defoe. Patrik Schick, who has been playing for current Bundesliga champions Bayer 04 Leverkusen since 2020, grew up in the Czech capital, Prague. He developed h

title: Bayer Leverkusen vs Borussia Dortmund - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: After winning the reverse fixture, Bayer 04 Leverkusen could now do a league double over Borussia Dortmund for the first time since 2006/07. However, their three-game wait at home for a victory against BVB in the Bundesliga is currently their longest against any top-flight side. Bayer 04 Leverkusen are unbeaten in their last seven Bundesliga games – only Union Berlin are currently enjoying a longer undefeated spell. However, B04’s 2-2 draw in Freiburg was their third draw in their last four games and their 11th overall in 2024/25, a joint league high together with RB Leipzig. Since 2000, the Werkself have only ever shared the points more often in a season in 2009/10.

title: Stuttgart vs Augsburg - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: VfB Stuttgart are unbeaten in their last seven competitive games against FC Augsburg, winning each of the last four without conceding a single goal. VfB won the most recent meeting 1-0 at home in the quarter-finals of the DFB-Pokal on 4th February 2025. Only FC Bayern have created more big chances this season than VfB Stuttgart, whereas FC Augsburg have had the fewest in the league – not even half as many as VfB.

title: Poitiers vs Tours - Marmara Spike ligue Volleyball 2024
description: The LNV Ligue A Masculine (LAM), currently known as the Marmara SpikeLigue for sponsorship reasons, is the top-tier mens volleyball league in France, established in 1938. Governed by the Ligue Nationale de Volley (LNV) under the French Volleyball Federation (FFVB), the league features Frances elite volleyball talent. Formerly called Pro A until 2009, it shares a rich history and prestige akin to its basketball counterpart.

description: Jeffs unconventional hunting lessons fail to prepare Bob and Screech to hunt game in the wild, but he discovers they may be learning on their own.

description: Discover how dogs have evolved from wild predators to friendly pets. Plus, a look at parts of the world where dogs are spoiled as much as children.

description: The Raneys attempt to save a single mother and her daughter from a rampant moose, Marty builds a bridge across a creek and Matt teaches predator deterrent techniques.

description: A family shares their crowded home with rescued animals, including two mini horses that sleep in the master bedroom! Antonio builds them the ultimate horse barn.

description: Terri returns to her hometown in Oregon to help Brady, a cougar in need of a health check. At the zoo, Bindi bathes an echidna with bad skin allergies.

description: Animal expert Coyote Peterson heads to cities including Alice Springs, Sydney and Darwin to track down and get close to the family of lizards known as dragons.

description: Animal expert Coyote Peterson treks deep into the Australian outback in search of the giant python, a non-venomous but still deadly snake.

description: Take a look back at the tanks ATM have built that were inspired by moments in history, including a 1920s mob-themed tank and a 1960s lava lamp tank.

description: The Browns try closing a deal to help restore a wind turbine, but when Browntown runs out of gas, they must get creative. Plus, Noah gets bad news from his girl.

description: Rob and vet Moose investigate a claim about dogfighting, while Brian and Face try to help an aggressive dog on a chain. Plus, Dori helps a homeless vet, and his cats.

description: Investigator McHugh finds a dog with a missing leg - what has happened to it? And investigator AJ is horrified by a puppy dying of tick infestation.

description: Robert takes on the challenge of relocating Bosco, the zoos most aggressive croc. Terri helps Harley the koala find love after a tough breeding season.

title: The Universe: Ancient Mysteries Solved: Pyramids
description: The Great Pyramids of Giza have eluded astronomers and archeologists for centuries. The worlds renowned Egyptologists, astronomers and engineers join forces to solve some of the long-held mysteries about the pyramids.

title: Buried: Knights Templar and the Holy Grail: Holy City, Holy Grail
description: A new investigation into the true fate of the Knights Templar is launched. Did the order really fall in 1307? Or did the powerful Knights continue on in secret? The team begins their investigation in Jerusalem, the epicentre of the Templars power.

title: Lost Worlds: Atlantis
description: In the heart of the Mediterranean, a peaceful island explodes with devastating force - it will be the biggest volcanic eruption in three and a half thousand years of recorded history.

description: Why did Asiana flight 214, packed with passengers, suddenly crash land and cartwheel across San Francisco International Airports runway? Three families of the dead want answers.

title: Clash of the Gods: Beowulf
description: The Viking worlds most famous warrior, the legend of Beowulf is the ultimate tale of courage.

title: Ancient Top 10: Ancient Sieges
description: The great empires of the ancient world were created through war, and the most defining battles were fought through siege warfare. From the legendary battle of Troy to the fall of Rome, which siege will top our list for being the most devastating?

title: Lost Gold Of World War II: Mud And Blood
description: With new evidence suggesting the location of a possible treasure vault beneath the waterfall, John is determined to find a way in, but mother nature is wreaking havoc on his plans. Meanwhile, a clue uncovered at Breach 6 has the team going all in.

title: Lost Relics of the Knights Templar: The Himmler Helmet

description: Most major geological processes require millions of year to become noticeable. Meteor impacts are exceptions which can cause comparable changes in seconds.

description: Examine the efforts under way to establish a human colony on Mars, including plans to grow food, recycle waste water and introduce a breathable atmosphere.

description: Explores the controversial theory that extraterrestrials have visited Earth. From the age of the dinosaurs to ancient Egypt.

description: An encounter in the American heartland indicates a disturbing twist to the UFO phenomenon. The team follows a trail of explosive evidence connecting UFOs to the most destructive weapons in human history.

title: Looting History: Risky Business: Michael Steinhardt...
description: ...and the Greek Pot of Gold: Michael Steinhardt, the largest private collector of antiquities, is forced to turn over $70 million dollars� worth of stolen loot and banned from collecting. His undoing comes after a four-year investigation known as Operation Demetra.

title: Pawn Stars Do America: Emerald City Adventures
description: Rick, Corey, and Chum are in Seattle, Washington. In between throwing fish at Pikes Market, the guys are hoping to find gems in the Emerald city, with a little help from their experts.

title: The Curse of Oak Island: On Target
description: After months of hard work, the Laginas once again descend the Garden Shaft and finally hit the tunnel theyve been chasing all year.

title: The Curse Of Oak Island: Dark and Stormy
description: While new discoveries across the island continue to invigorate the team, a dangerous storm threatens to shut down the entire operation.

description: As the team makes contact with the elusive tunnel under the Garden Shaft, an exciting new scientific theory surfaces which suggests a connection between Nolans Cross and the Knights Templar.

description: ...Sasquatch: Is this home security video proof that UFOs are messing with our technology? Did a visitor at a historic cemetery in Savannah capture home video of a ghost child? A metal detectorist claims to have recorded the sound a hungry Bigfoot.

title: The Proof Is Out There: Mutant Mermaid, UFOs vs Nukes and Seamonster...

description: Chum gets his hands on a trio of vintage comic strip characters; will the seller play with his emotions, and toy around with a deal? Next, a book by Amelia Earhart flies into the shop. Will Rick dare to make a deal, or will the price soar too high?

title: Prison Chronicles: Dannemora
description: Dannemora, located in the frigid Adirondack mountains, its nickname is "little Siberia." Officially called the Clinton Correctional facility, this foreboding prison is commonly known as Dannemora, named after the town where it is built.

title: Prison Chronicles: San Quentin
description: San Quentin located in Marin County on the San Francisco Bay is Californias oldest prison dating back to the gold rush, and home to the states only gas chamber. Here three men have tried to find their way out of the prisons clutches.

title: The UnXplained With William Shatner: Secrets of Ancient Structures
description: Scattered across the globe lie mysterious ruins. These age-old structures stand as silent sentinels from the past, their true history seemingly erased by time. Can modern archaeology unravel the enigma of how - and why - these wonders were built?

title: Forged In Fire: Gladiators Of The Forge: A Champions Quest
description: Our defending champion currently has four wins under his belt but will face his toughest challenge yet in forging the very weapon used to assassinate Julius Caesar, the Pugio Dagger.

title: Looting History: Making A Killing: Douglas Latchford...
description: ...and the Cambodian Killing Fields: As Douglas Latchford is accused of masterminding a multimillion-dollar racket in loot stolen from Cambodias killing fields, museums and collectors face the grim reality that theyre in possession of stolen property.

title: The Curse Of Oak Island: On Their Marks
description: Rick, Marty, and the team return to Oak Island and immediately uncover evidence of a mysterious tunnel in the Money Pit.

title: American Pickers: The Diy Delorean
description: Mike meets someone who shares his passion for vintage treasures, this leads him to a space filled with items that seem to be untouched by time.

title: Pawn Stars: Off the Rails
description: Chum gets his hands on a trio of vintage comic strip characters; will the seller play with his emotions, and toy around with a deal? Next, a book by Amelia Earhart flies into the shop. Will Rick dare to make a deal, or will the price soar too high?

title: River Hunters: Salisbury
description: River Hunters sees Rick and river expert Beau searching the unexplored rivers and waterways of Britain, unearthing treasures from the past which reveal how ancestors used to live.

title: River Hunters: The Battle of Killiecrankie
description: The team find evidence from one of Scotlands bloodiest eras as they wade through the waters of the River Garry in the Scottish Highlands, the site of the first major clash between Highland Jacobites and the government army.

title: River Hunters: Viking Invasion
description: Rick and Beau tackle the mighty River Ouse in Yorkshire, hunting for evidence of Britain’s most notorious sea-faring raiders - the Vikings. With a find potentially dating to the 11th Century battle, it’s a river hunt of epic proportions.

title: Looting History: Making A Killing: Douglas Latchford...
description: ...and the Cambodian Killing Fields: As Douglas Latchford is accused of masterminding a multimillion-dollar racket in loot stolen from Cambodias killing fields, museums and collectors face the grim reality that theyre in possession of stolen property.

title: The Curse Of Oak Island: On Their Marks
description: Rick, Marty, and the team return to Oak Island and immediately uncover evidence of a mysterious tunnel in the Money Pit.

title: American Pickers: The Diy Delorean
description: Mike meets someone who shares his passion for vintage treasures, this leads him to a space filled with items that seem to be untouched by time.

title: Pawn Stars: Off the Rails
description: Chum gets his hands on a trio of vintage comic strip characters; will the seller play with his emotions, and toy around with a deal? Next, a book by Amelia Earhart flies into the shop. Will Rick dare to make a deal, or will the price soar too high?

title: Ross Kemp: Deep Sea Treasure Hunter: Suez
description: Fresh from diving on the Mary Rose and still on the hunt for underwater artefacts that tell the story of the British Empire, Ross hops round the coast from Portsmouth to Plymouth, then on to the Gulf of Suez.

title: Ross Kemp: Deep Sea Treasure Hunter: Nazi Menace
description: In this episode Ross continues his diving quest in the crystal clear waters of the Red Sea off the coast of Egypt. It’s a deeply personal journey as Ross’ grandfather fought in the North Africa campaign during World War Two.

title: Ross Kemp: Deep Sea Treasure Hunter: D-Day
description: Ross goes on the hunt for wrecks that tell the story of D-Day, the 1944 Allied invasion of Occupied France, and discovers how winning wasn’t just a case of superior firepower and numbers, but also ingenuity.

title: Ross Kemp: Shipwreck Treasure Hunter: The U-Boat Terror
description: Ross completes his specialist SCUBA training under the expert tutelage of dive Supervisor Neil Brock, and inspired by the stories of his shipwrecked relatives, he heads up to the Royal Navy’s historic naval base in the far northerly Orkney Islands.

title: Mystery Places: Episode 12
description: Explore the most dangerous hotel in the world, visit the housing development in Luoyang, China - a copy of an Austrian UNESCO village - and check out the most fascinating beaches in the world.

title: The Curse Of Oak Island: Across The Pond
description: While on a research mission in England, Marty, Alex, and Charles are thrilled to uncover more evidence connecting the Knights Templar to the Oak Island mystery.

title: American Pickers: Carnival Crash Out
description: In Minnesota, Mike and Jersey go hog wild for a four-generation carny collection complete with carousel horses, toy tanks, and bumper cars. Down the road in New Hampshire, on a special mission for Robbie, the guys head to Rogers analogue laboratory.

title: Pawn Stars: Wanted: Pawned or Alive
description: Rick is ready for some football when a Super Bowl bucket hat rushes into the shop. Can he score big, or will he fumble the deal? Corey and Chum are envious when Spencer brings in an Incredible Hulk comic book. Will their strongest offer be enough?

title: The Curse Of Oak Island: The Chosen
description: Rick, Marty, and the Oak Island team go in-depth with Matty Blake on locations where they hope to unearth buried treasure in the Money Pit area.

title: Beyond Skinwalker Ranch: Tumbleweeds And Uaps
description: Andy and Paul investigate a desert hotbed of strange activity where local lore speaks of an entity called "Goldie", they find that not only is there scientific evidence backing up these stories, but other entities may not want these stories told.

title: Forged In Fire: Gladiators Of The Forge: The Final Battles
description: Its back to the Colosseum for the last two one-on-one battles. The reigning champion has defeated six opponents, but now must face a returning challenger and forge the intricate acinaces sword.

title: Ross Kemp: Shipwreck Treasure Hunter: The U-Boat Terror
description: Ross completes his specialist SCUBA training under the expert tutelage of dive Supervisor Neil Brock, and inspired by the stories of his shipwrecked relatives, he heads up to the Royal Navy’s historic naval base in the far northerly Orkney Islands.
